data.text:
Thank you so much Toni and the team of Cornwells at Weeping Cross. So glad that you like Repeat Flow and that Nas has been able to provide you with support. Toni "Today I had over the phone training with Naz, regarding repeat flow with my our pharmacy Cornwells Weeping Cross. All aspects of Repeat flow were fully explained in a manner I could easily understand, all my questions were answers, Naz was very knowledgeable and happy to help me nothing was to much trouble. Repeat Flow platform seems amazing and I am looking forward to using within the Pharmacy to improve services to our patients." Thank you once again for choosing Titan—we look forward to continuing this journey of innovation and support together! Feel free to explore more about Titan on our website: www.titanpmr.com #CustomerAppreciation #PharmacyInnovation #HealthTech #DigitalPharmacy #communitypharmacy #pmr #pmrreimagined #support #titanpmr #repeatflow

#DeltaSurgical are excited to invite you to our very first FREE #webinar 'Targeted Temperature Management: Illness Severity’ on Wednesday, September 20.
